{"$category":"crawled","mainimg":"http://file8.mafengwo.net/M00/F3/BD/wKgByU-s9zWT9iLyAAUSkpwqZSI60.book.w230.jpeg","addname":"傩舞","tags":"<span>傩舞</span>\n                <div class=\"clear\"></div>","abstracts":"<p><strong>简介</strong> 傩起源于原始社会的狩猎、图腾崇拜、巫术意识。周代傩被纳入国家礼制。先秦文献记载，傩礼是希望调理四时阴阳，以求寒暑相宜，风调雨顺，五谷丰登，人畜平安，国富民生。汉唐时宫廷大傩仪式尤为隆重，并传入越南、朝鲜半岛和日本。北宋末期宫廷傩礼采用新制，傩开始出现戏曲化和娱乐化倾向。元代，因蒙人信仰的不同，傩礼受到排斥。明代恢复过宫傩，傩舞虽古意犹存，但到了清代却逐渐在宫廷消失。而《论语?乡党》中记载的“乡人傩”一直在民间延续，并转化为娱乐性的风俗活动，且与民间一些迎神赛社活动混融一体，呈现出多种傩仪淆杂的局面。傩祀风习至今仍在我国广大农村流行，尤以江西乡野保存较为完好，古风犹存。</p>","imgs":"<li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"0\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file8.mafengwo.net/M00/F3/BD/wKgByU-s9zWT9iLyAAUSkpwqZSI60.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"1\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file7.mafengwo.net/M00/F3/BE/wKgByU-s9zfBFlV6AAYy-zkDQfY10.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"2\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file7.mafengwo.net/M00/F3/C0/wKgByU-s9zmooQrLAAYcvl9zuVQ81.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"3\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file8.mafengwo.net/M00/F3/C1/wKgByU-s